title: War of the Roses - She Didn't Post ANYTHING at the Pumpkin Patch
description: Lindsay asked Karissa to hang out but Karissa said she had plans to go to a pumpkin patch. Here's the catch, she didn't post a single thing. Lindsay is confused because who goes to a pumpkin patch and doesn't post anything?! Karissa ended up bringing something home that was CLEARLY not from the patch. And there was a HUGE surprise when we called her..
